data.description: NEW GARAGE DOOR 2023! ROOF & WATER HEATER-2022! HVAC-2021! With an acceptable offer, sellers will provide $8000 in a credit to buyers to use at their discretion!! Located in the Mendenhall subsection of SP, this home is a GEM! On a cul-de-sac lot, this home boasts an extra parking pad to the right of the driveway! Inside it offers a very large & cozy living room with a fireplace & hearth. All bedrooms are upstairs & the front room over the garage (FROG) serves as the 4th bedroom, playroom, man cave, etc. Back deck was extended in '20 to maximize outdoor entertainment.  An expansive back yard backing up to woods provides not only a shed & privacy, but many other options.
